# Web Summarizer

![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/Python-3.x-blue)
![OpenAI](https://img.shields.io/badge/OpenAI-API-orange)
![Status](https://img.shields.io/badge/Status-Active-brightgreen)

A lightweight tool that scrapes any webpage and generates an AI-powered summary using OpenAI models. Perfect for quickly digesting articles, blogs, and news content.

---

## Features

- **Web Scraping** – Extracts main content from a given URL.
- **AI Summarization** – Summarizes content using OpenAI LLM.
- **Environment Variables** – Keeps your API keys secure.
- **CLI Friendly** – Simple command-line execution.
- **Extendable** – Can be used in larger automation workflows.

---

## Tech Stack

- **Python 3**
- `requests`, `beautifulsoup4` – Web scraping
- `openai` – AI summarization
- `python-dotenv` – Environment variable management

---

## Installation

### 1. Clone the repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/Arijeet223/web-summarizer.git
cd web-summarizer
